ghts tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u derby th\u00e0nh Madrid Real vs Atletico v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18 l\u00fac 21h15 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 8/4.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: Real 0-0 Atletico</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh Madrid nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 v\u1eabn di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. Hai tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec Atletico d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Diego Simeone v\u1eabn tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eb7t, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 \u0111i theo l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t cao. Nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Bernabeu hay qua truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tranh \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc duy nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn derby l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. Real l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Atletico khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 l\u1ea7n bao g\u1ed3m 2 \u0111i tr\u00fang khung g\u1ed7 song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 pha b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas c\u1ee7a Real.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nReal Madrid: </strong>Keylor; Carvajal, Varane, Ramos, Marcelo; Lucas, Kovacic, Kroos, Asensio; Ronaldo, Bale.<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico: </strong>Oblak; Juanfran, Savic, God\u00edn, Lucas; Vitolo, Sa\u00fal, Thomas, Koke; Griezmann, Diego Costa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>G.V (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"923","checkdouble":"183822"},{"date":"22:30 08/04","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/thay-gi-sau-chien-thang-day-kich-tinh-cua-arsenal-truoc-southampton.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;back