c Athletic Bilbao v\u00e0 Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League v\u1edbi AS Roma, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Sergio Busquets b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9n \u0111au ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 t\u1edbi n\u1eeda sau hi\u1ec7p 2, anh c\u0169ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Paulinho. Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leganes r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (8/4), Busquets kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Busquets binh phuc chan thuong truoc tran vs Roma hinh anh\" title=\"Busquets b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn vs Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Busquets-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-tran-vs-Roma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Busquets ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBusi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, Barca \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t vui: Sergio Busquets b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Olimpico c\u1ee7a Blaugrana, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t vui b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Barca c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u1edfng Busquets ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leganes l\u00e0 h\u01a1i s\u1edbm song khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Roma, d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh Busquets s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Busquets tro lai o CL\" title=\"Busquets tro lai o CL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Busquets-tro-lai-o-CL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Busquets b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 21 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Roma r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 4 t\u1edbi (11/4):</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Ter Stegen, Ortola, Cillessen<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Semedo, Pique, Alba, Umtiti, Mina, Vermaelen, Roberto<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Rakitic, Busquets, D.Suarez, Iniesta, Paulinho, Gomes, Vidal<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: L.Suarez, Messi, Dembele, Alcacer<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\