s:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Antoine Griezmann ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Barca quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/atletico-madrid-1390.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atletico Madrid</strong></span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duoc Barca va MU de y, Antoine Griezmann phat bieu ve tuong lai hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca v\u00e0 MU \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd, Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Duoc-Barca-va-MU-de-y,-Antoine-Griezmann-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nDon Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Griezmann c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-bat-ngo-tim-nha-o-thanh-pho-barcelona-180-179544.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona</strong></span>. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan, anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n l\u00e0 sai s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c. Th\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c m\u00e0 n\u00f3i t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 quan t\u00e2m b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Atletico Madrid mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf Europa League v\u00e0 La Liga, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Antoine Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi VCK World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann vs Leganes\" title=\"Griezmann vs Leganes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/griezmann-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dam-phan-voi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, t\u00f4i\u00a0kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec1u tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/antoine-griezmann-44452.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Griezmann</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 anh b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/85859-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"920","checkdouble":"183819"},{"date":"21:04