 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n,...<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi bong cua Cong Vinh bi che vi he thong bien quang cao dien tu.\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh b\u1ecb ch\u00ea v\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/lap-bien-quang-cao-dien-tu-doi-bong-cua-cong-vinh-bi-che-trach.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh b\u1ecb ch\u00ea v\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB TP.HCM ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o LED n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1o ra \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean Bongdaplus: &quot;&ldquo;H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n LED qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y xung quanh s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhanh v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1eb7c s\u1ee1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n&quot;.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea1y gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t n\u00f3 xa m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau khi va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi nhau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ng\u00e3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra m\u1eaft h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, CLB TP.HCM thu v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/bang-xep-hang-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">BXH V-League 2018</span></span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-bong-cua-cong-vinh-bi-cdv-tphcm-la-o-168-183624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/doi-bong-cua-cong-vinh-bi-cdv-tphcm-la-o.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-bong-cua-cong-vinh-bi-cdv-tphcm-la-o-168-183624.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh b\u1ecb C\u0110V TP.HCM la \u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua SLNA</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t, thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c C\u0110V la \u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 1 V-League v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"918","checkdouble":"183801"},{"date":"11:06 08/04","title":"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh m\u1ea5t bao l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/5/chan-thuong-cua-duy-manh-phai-nghi-thi-dau-bao-lau.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepanne