afp \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Neymar?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin toi 0804 Pogba sap doi cho Neymar hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 0804 Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Pogba v\u00e0 Martial n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Anthony Martial cho PSG n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sheffield Wednesday</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, M.U \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 19 tu\u1ed5i George Hirst c\u1ee7a Sheffield Wednesday, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Leicester, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Watford ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Richarlison</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mirror th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Watford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Richarlison n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o chi ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, PSG, Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Max Allegri t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf London</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Max Allegri\" title=\"Max Allegri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/hlv-moi-cua-chelsea-dang-tim-nha-o-london.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Max Allegri t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf London</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Max Allegri c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London, \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng s\u1eafp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Isco b\u00e1o tin vui cho Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Man City \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Bale c\u00e2u Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Liverpool nh\u1ea3 Mohamed Salah, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Kop nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Van Dijk tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Van Dijk va Jesus\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Van Dijk va Jesus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Man-City-vs-Liverpool-Van-Dijk-va-Jesus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van Dijk tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Kop s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"916","checkdouble":"183821"},{"date":"10:43 08/04","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/real-madrid-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{f