agonal-se{background-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid thay th\u1ebf Zinedine Zidane, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 Los Blancos.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Real Madrid \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Champions League. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i PSG 5-2 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Juventus 3-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Los Blancos \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp dan dat Real Madrid thay Zinedine Zidane hinh anh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid thay Zinedine Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Jurgen-Klopp-dan-dat-Real-Madrid-thay-Zinedine-Zidane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, song th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/zinedine-zidane-145.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Zidane </strong></span>s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd tr\u1eafng tay, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. BL\u0110 Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Zidane ho\u1eb7c t\u1ef1 \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec7 \u0111\u01a1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u00e2m th\u1ea7m ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCR7 t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c Zidane kh\u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh gi\u1ecfi l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay HLV Zidane</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y Real \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Zidane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Bernabeu n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real nham Klopp thay Zidane\" title=\"Real nh\u1eafm Klopp thay Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/real-madrid-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid thay Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid </strong></span>thay th\u1ebf Zinedine Zidane, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 Los Blancos. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKlopp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Dortmund v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga 2 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang gi\u00fap Liverpool tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Dortmund. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Klopp, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-hlv-mauricio-pochettino-thay-zidane-180-178843.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Pochettino </strong></span>c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"",