\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Atletico 2 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam th\u1ee9 3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0</strong></span> ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Juventus t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. 48 gi\u1edd sau, Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sporting Lisbon 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Wanda Metropolitano. T\u1ed1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf tr\u1eadn El Derbi madrileno.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Real c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf 2 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Atletico. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos sa s\u00fat \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y khi c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9, c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zidane kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ly do tin tran derby Madrid Real vs Atletico nghieng ve Ken ken hinh anh\" title=\"L\u00fd do tin tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Atletico-Madrid-v-Real-Madrid-Carvajal-tranh-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Atletico v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Atletico l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thong dong \u0111\u00f3. Ngay sau khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Sporting t\u1ea1i Europa League, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ngay. S\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico l\u00e0 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nAtletico b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o derby c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. T\u1ea1i La Liga, ngay c\u1ea3 khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i Santiago Bernabeu, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Barcelona t\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m (th\u1eafng Leganes 3-1 \u0111\u00eam qua). V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Barca, Atletico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y tia s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, Europa League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Atletico gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i La Liga, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean &ldquo;c\u01a1m ch\u00e1o&rdquo;. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 s\u1ea9y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sporting, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico vs Sporting Costa\" title=\"Atletico vs Sporting Costa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Atletico-vs-Sporting.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Costa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 l\u00e0 Europa League kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1eeba th\u00e3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. T\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014 t\u1edbi nay, tr\u1ea3i qua 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u1ec1n, Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League m\u00f9a 2012/13, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Diego Simeone th\u1eeba th\u1eafng \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i La Liga ngay m\u00f9a sau. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Real \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eddi, m\u1ed9t v\u1ef1c. Con s\u1ed1 12 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 11 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. \u0110\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kinh ho\u00e0ng cho Real th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed1p 4 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tap the Real khong tam thuong\" title=\"tap the Real khong tam thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/tap-the-Real-khong-tam-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng La Liga c\u1ee7a Atletico 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 1 di\u1ec3m n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf derby. T\u1ea1i Champions League, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-tran-dai-chien-mot-chieu-juve-vs-real-184-183478.html\"><strong>Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus 3-0</strong></span> ngay t\u1ea1i Turin khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e0ng tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1ec3 s\u1ee3. T\u1eeb t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb trung tuy\u1ebfn cho t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9t nh\u1eadp hai c\u00e1nh, B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng. H\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111ang l\u00ean cao, kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd g\u00ec Real kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m kh\u00f3 \u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e2n s\u0129 kh\u00ed h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch bao nhi\u00eau h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi-184-183504.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i ca t\u1ee5ng anh b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 tr\u1edf \u0111i. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd l\u00e0&hellip; \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh tinh kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo noi ve tran Juventus vs Real Madrid\" title=\"Ronaldo n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Juventus vs Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/du-am-juventus-vs-real-khi-messi-moi-qua-nho-be-so-voi-cr7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 23 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t 0,96 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn, t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Lionel Messi (0,90 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn). Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, song CR7 th\u00ec c\u00f2n s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nXa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn derby Madrid Real vs Atletico c\u00f2n gi\u00fap Ronaldo ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha &ldquo;ti\u1ebfn h\u00f3a&rdquo; tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. D\u00f9 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o, anh c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n ghi b\u00e0n cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"Preview Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/real-madrid-vs-atletico-madrid-21h15-ngay-84-derby-mau-trang.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid 21h15 ng\u00e0y 8/4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Real Madrid vs Atletico\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Real Madrid vs Atletico\" src=\"https://