ea3 \u0111\u0169a Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean BXH La Liga l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Barcelona \u0111ang c\u00f3 12 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 Atletico Madrid (ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 tr\u1eadn). N\u1ebfu Atletico th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby t\u1ed1i nay (8/4), kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh r\u1eb1ng cho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn El Clasico tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Camp Nou, n\u1ebfu Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp th\u00e0nh hai h\u00e0ng, v\u1ed7 tay ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga. C\u00f2n m\u1ed9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique phat bieu ve Real va Zidane truoc El Clasico hinh anh\" title=\"Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc El Clasico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Pique-phat-bieu-ve-Real-va-Zidane-truoc-El-Clasico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Zinedine Zidane, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/zidane-quyet-khong-cho-real-chuc-mung-barca-180-183737.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3</strong></span>. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00ednh Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Real khi h\u1ecd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FIFA Club World Cup h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pique m\u1ec9a mai Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGerard Pique kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ef1c m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zidane \u0111\u01b0a ra. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean m\u1ec9a mai Real Madrid nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay \u0111\u00e2y!\u201d, Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 Zidane sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leganes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique noi ve Real\" title=\"Pique noi ve Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/gerard-pique-phat-bieu-ve-real-va-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Real v\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ec9a mai<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Barca n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i La Liga l\u00ean 38 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00ednh t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. V\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Pique n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cK\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u01a1i ch\u00f9ng xu\u1ed1ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a BXH.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-barca-31-leganes-vong-31-la-liga-201718-328-183776.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-1 Leganes (V\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-barca-vs-leganes-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718-180-183766.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Barca vs Leganes tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-leganes-01h45-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183740.html\">Barca 3-1 Leganes (KT): C\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a Messilona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/zidane-quyet-khong-cho-real-chuc-mung-barca-180-183737.html\">Zidane quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng cho Real ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Barca</spa