ng>Andre Gomes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca</strong></span> t\u1eeb Valencia \u1edf H\u00e8 2016 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU va Man City vao cuoc, Andre Gomes phat bieu ve tuong lai hinh anh\" title=\"MU v\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, Andre Gomes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/16/MU-va-Man-City-vao-cuoc,-Andre-Gomes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Andre Gomes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong 2 n\u0103m \u1edf Barca c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd trong hai k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Barca, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/mu-chu-y-barca-giam-gia-ban-andre-gomes-180-165500.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U quan t\u00e2m Gomes</strong></span>, Tottenham, Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Valencia n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gomes l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes phat bieu ve tuong lai\" title=\"Andre Gomes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/andre-gomes-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cNgay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Barca h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng\u00a0danh hi\u1ec7u, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Barca kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/andre-gomes-54489.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Andre Gomes</strong></span> ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o: \u201cNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 M.U hay Tottenham l\u00e0 sai s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andre Gomes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/235460-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andre Gomes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"911","checkdouble":"183818"},{"date":"17:57 08/04","title":"B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, sao Man City kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAd