 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn 2 b\u00e0n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU v\u00ec l\u00fd do sau \u0111\u00e2y.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea1m 1 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e1t vang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. 2-3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 Man City s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi l\u1ea1i l\u1ecbch \u0103n m\u1eebng. Qu\u00e1 cay c\u00fa, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean City TV, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. V\u00ec sao \u01b0? B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00ec bi\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i, h\u1ecd ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i theo m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, phong \u0111\u1ed9, nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\" title=\"Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i cho b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i &ndash; h\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng nhau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng nhau nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League. Danilo ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU v\u00ec ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f2n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Paul Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khen-ngoi-bo-ba-cua-mu-sau-dai-thang-man-city-172-183809.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/mourinho-khen-ngoi-bo-ba-cua-mu-sau-dai-thang-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khen-ngoi-bo-ba-cua-mu-sau-dai-thang-man-city-172-183809.html\">Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ee7a MU sau \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchester r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda t\u1ea1i Etihad \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn derby Manchester th\u1ee9 176 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City vs MU 2-3, d\u00f9 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"910","checkdouble":"183813"},{"date":"18:10 08/04","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1, Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/3-yeu-to-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-kinh-dien-truoc-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{paddi