u00e0 c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Frank Lampard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, d\u1eabu h\u1ecd ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi 3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7p 2 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 Lampard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 97 gi\u00e2y ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Chris Smalling \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-2 cho Man United. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u. N\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda n\u00e0o cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lampard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchestert\" title=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/de-tro-thanh-so-1-pogba-can-phai-lam-dieu-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lampard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba sau tr\u1eadn derby Manchestert</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f4i khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u, thay v\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00f4i khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Frank Lampard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i gi\u1ed1ng nhau n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 (l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3), Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Frank Lampard m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng Pogba l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 m\u00e0u m\u00e8 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 trong&nbsp;hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Lampard n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u00f4 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU 2-3</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-tran-cau-kinh-dien-man-city-vs-mu-172-183765.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn derby kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Man City 2-3 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ruc-sang-tran-derby-pogba-van-bi-nguoi-mu-chi-trich-172-183773.html\">R\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn derby, Pogba v\u1eabn b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi MU ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quat-nga-man-city-mou-tien-the-to-pep-la-ke-doi-tra-172-183772.html\">Qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City, Mou ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1 Pep l\u00e0 k\u1ebb d\u1ed1i tr\u00e1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Manchester</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"909","checkdouble":"183814"},{"date":"18:09 08/04","title":"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap MU ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/3-yeu-to-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-kinh-dien-truoc-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adC