lor:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i derby th\u00e0nh Manchester, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ed9ng ra, \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Sir Alex Ferguson huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i (n\u0103m 2013). T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7, 4, 5, 6 v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ryan Giggs \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn derby Manchester v\u1eeba qua, khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Matchday Live, khi m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Ian Wright (Arsenal) cho r\u1eb1ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, Ryan Giggs \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u00fd ki\u1ebfn n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ef1u Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Giggs cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a sau l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League\" title=\"Giggs cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a sau l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/huyen-thoai-mu-chung-toi-se-vo-dich-mua-giai-sau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giggs cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a sau l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n 40% nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, MU \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn Man City, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Giggs ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Man United s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, Man City s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u1ede trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi, khi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd&rdquo; &ndash; Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Man United ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh d\u1ef1, b\u1edfi Man xanh v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t xa. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng g\u00e3 h\u1ec1, khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u1ed3n \u00e0o l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs MU<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830134/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Man City vs MU<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU 2-3<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-tro-thanh-so-1-pogba-can-phai-lam-dieu-nay-172-183814.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1, Pogba c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-de-dau-cuoi-co-sao-man-city-khong-phuc-chien-thang-cua-mu-172-183813.html\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ed5, sao Man City kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-psg-pogba-martial-neymar-172-183797.html\">MU g\u1eedi PSG: Pogba + Martial = Neymar?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep-172-183779.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Manchester</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-noi-gi-de-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-kinh-dien-truoc-man-city-172-183768.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap MU ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"907","checkdouble":"183816"},{"date":"19:58 08/04","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/5/van-dijk-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@fo