ackground-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c an to\u00e0n khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man City gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau. Nh\u01b0ng Virgil van Dijk ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t hay. V\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh b\u00ean kia v\u00e0 ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 sau 31 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-liverpool-30-man-city-bo-mat-khac-thuong-cua-lu-doan-do-184-183594.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>3-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Liverpool</strong></span> c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Kop th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi v\u1ed1n li\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HLV Klopp s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng khi g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Dijk phat bieu truoc tran Man City vs Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"Van Dijk ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Van-Dijk-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Man-City-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool th\u1eafng Man City t\u1edbi 3-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng Van Dijk l\u1ea1i ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVirgil van Dijk kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 nh\u01b0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Van Dijk ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan n\u00f3i tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Liverpool. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u0103m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n song t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah Liverpool vs Man City\" title=\"Salah Liverpool vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/van-dijk-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-man-city-vs-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">Van Dijk ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng s\u1ebd L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (7/4), Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton \u1edf derby Merseyside v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tran-everton-00-liverpool-172-183778.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>h\u00f2a 0-0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a</strong></span>. Van Dijk ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Etihad v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton khi m\u00e0 3 ng\u00e0y sau l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Champions League\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn song \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi n\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</stron