l,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Tr\u1eadn derby Manchester th\u1ee9 176 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City vs MU 2-3, d\u00f9 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong serie phim truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;Tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i V\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ec1n&rdquo;, th\u1ea7y d\u1ea1y ki\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt Arya c\u00f3 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u nh\u01b0 sau: &ldquo;<em>Ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Th\u1ea7n Ch\u1ebft th\u00f4i? </em><strong><em>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay</em></strong>!&rdquo; (Not Today).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Man-City-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City</span> c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t, m\u1ed9t Th\u1ea7n Ch\u1ebft reo r\u1eafc s\u1ef1 kinh ho\u00e0ng tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eeba th\u00e3i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Man xanh, khi c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ef3 d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf h\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn), c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-tran-cau-kinh-dien-man-city-vs-mu-172-183765.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City vs MU</span>, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0103n m\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"C\u0110V Man City \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/mancuty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&quot;Pep l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, c\u00f2n Mourinho l\u00e0 k\u1ebb h\u1ebft th\u1eddi&quot;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pep kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Vincent Kompany c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng (\u0111\u1eadm) \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 vui m\u1eebng khi ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 &ldquo;c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3&rdquo;, khi Man xanh s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n sau 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Pep Guardiola m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Gundogan, khi \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong t\u1ea7m tay. Kompany, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/chris-smalling-43838.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chris Smalling</span> t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">7 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, so v\u1edbi 0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, so v\u1edbi 0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u1edf trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1eb1ng 3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a n\u1ed5i Raheem Sterling. Thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 tranh ch\u1ea5p, b\u1ecb \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c &ldquo;b\u1eb9p d\u00ed&rdquo; \u1edf n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling hi\u1ec7p 1 Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling trong hi\u1ec7p 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/sma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling trong hi\u1ec7p 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Khi Paul Pogba n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tung c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ea7u may b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m <strong>\u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN</strong> c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y (ph\u00fat 58). Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Ilkay Gundogan khi\u1ebfn fan Man United th\u00f3t tim v\u1edbi pha c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng li\u1ebfm khung g\u1ed7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t tia s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o cho n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong c\u00e1i ng\u00e0y Sir Alex Ferguson \u0111\u1ebfn Etihad ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ea7n ch\u1ebft Man City &ndash; b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh&rdquo;</em> &ndash; T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 Smalling cho bi\u1ebft trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. <em>&ldquo;HLV kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng, li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u0169 h\u1ec1 nh\u00ecn Man City l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch hay kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, khi Man United v\u00f9ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling hi\u1ec7p 2 Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba v\u00e0 Smalling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/smal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong hi\u1ec7p 2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh x\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 97 gi\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/paul-pogba-44584.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Pogba</span> k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn derby Manchester tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, trong \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a anh. Chris Smalling sau \u0111\u00f3, s\u1eeda sai c\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m, \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c m\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u1edbc phim tua ch\u1eadm, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Vincent Kompany v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh Chris Smalling \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch anh \u0111em v\u1ec1 ngai v\u00e0ng cho Man City v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh Kompany \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, c\u0169ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n quen thu\u1ed9c. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Gundogan v\u00e0 Sterling bi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong hi\u1ec7p 2. T\u1eeb gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, s\u1ed1 6 chuy\u1ec1n cho s\u1ed1 7, v\u00e0 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n. M\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/du-am-man-city-23-mu-khong-phai-hom-nay-dau-pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pep trong tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2, Man xanh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t CLB ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ander Herrera &ldquo;gi\u1ea3 ch\u1ebft&rdquo; sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m, Pogba ng\u0103n \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u00eau kh\u00edch Man City.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City vs MU</span>&nbsp;</span>\u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Man xanh g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Man \u0111\u1ecf v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i (17 v\u00e0 9), c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn (6 v\u00e0 3). M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, v\u00e0 h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed7i ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng&hellip; ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Pep Guardiola v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, r\u1eb1ng Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u00ea th\u1ea3m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt ra Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p tr\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e2u, Pep!&rdquo;&nbsp;<br>\r\n</strong></em> &nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City vs MU: 2-3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City: Kompany (25&rsquo;), Gundogan (31&rsquo;)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU: Pogba (53&rsquo;, 55&rsquo;), Smalling (69&rsquo;)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Man City vs MU 2-3</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/11830134/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Man City 2-3 MU<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/Thang-nguoc-Man-City-2-3-MU,-Mou-tien-the-to-Pep-la-ke-doi-tra-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-o-tran-derby-manchester-172-183775.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby Manchester</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Man City vs MU 2-3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-tran-cau-kinh-dien-man-city-vs-mu-172-183765.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/ruc-sang-tran-derby-pogba-van-bi-nguoi-mu-chi-trich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-tran-cau-kinh-dien-man-city-vs-mu-172-183765.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn derby kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Man City 2-3 MU</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn derby Manchester gi\u1eefa Man City vs MU, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"905","checkdouble":"183779"},{"date":"09:09 08/04","title":"Thua MU, Pep \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/thua-mu-pep-do-loi-cho-hang-thu.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(No