 nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool \u1edf Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pogba Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Premier-League-Manchester-City-vs-Manchester-United.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 nh\u1edd hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vincent Kompany v\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Smalling mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, d\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City, song NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-man-city-vs-mu-tran-derby-thanh-manchester-vong-33-premier-league-201718-172-183742.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Man City 2-3 MU</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad, sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield th\u00ec h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u1eefa. Man xanh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Liverpool \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/pep-guardiola-88.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Pep Guardiola</strong></span> n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Man xanh tr\u1eafng tay t\u1ea1i Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola noi ve tran Man City vs MU\" title=\"Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/thua-mu-pep-do-loi-cho-hang-thu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Song hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat M.U c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, Pep chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Man City s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video Man City 2-3 MU (V\u00f2ng 33 Premier League 2017/18)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"904","checkdouble":"183791"}]}